{"tid":1969684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實 班大陸狗嘈交點解可以咁撚廢?","createTime":"2020-04-12T14:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T17:36:32.000Z","uid":35562,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c4aa0210e9ad21c52758376e85bf599fc61cad32","tid":1969684,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:54:40.000Z","msg":"睇d泰國tweet留言 佢地d「反擊」不外乎<br />\n1. 你媽死了<br />\n2. 你個國家好窮 / 你個泰王好垃圾<br />\n<br />\n淨係講1 其實我真係諗唔明句野有幾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人每日唔知講幾多次屌你老母<br />\n但你同D大陸狗講NMSL佢地又唔知點解真係會嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你兜口兜口同我講你老母死左我個反應應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2就唔洗講啦 我諗全世界得佢地會驚人講自己政府唔好<br />\n全世界應該冇1個政府係冇比人日屌夜屌<br />\n<br />\n之前D帝吧出征原來就係周圍貼熊貓STICKER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心唔明佢地有咩勇氣學人周圍挑機 黎黎去去都係得「NMSL」"},{"pid":"b1d3594b7e9f166665e3a080da979fb300337e23","tid":1969684,"uid":175079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"香港人而家放假冇野做，唔該去twitter幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f263e57fa1b9b16b89785a25afc3ac796991e1da","tid":1969684,"uid":197149,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"佢地本身玻璃心，喺圍牆下無乜幽默感，來來去去只係笑無謂嘢<br />\n以為鬧人老豆老母同國家，人地會同佢地一樣嬲到氣絕身亡<br />\n<br />\n其實我地都要學下泰國<br />\n同五毛小粉紅嘈唔好太認真太上心<br />\n佢地鬧乜我地都當無到，淨係用佢地差嗰面反映就得"},{"pid":"de97c3acaacb868db6369ad60b7324546c4f8cef","tid":1969684,"uid":107577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:00:12.000Z